 should be closely monitored for hepatotoxicity.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/128633/', '', 'Chondroitin sulfate, Esomeprazole, Glucosamine', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, More', 1767369485);
